[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":690},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fpython\u002F20210930\u002F691102834\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fpython\u002F20210930\u002F691102834\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fpython\u002F20210930\u002F691102834\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fpython\u002F20210930\u002F691102834\u002F":669,"related:\u002Fpython\u002F20210930\u002F691102834\u002F":678},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F30\u002Fpython-29-beautifulsoup\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":652,"date":653,"description":18,"extension":654,"lang":655,"meta":656,"navigation":147,"path":657,"readingMinutes":658,"seo":659,"standalone":660,"stem":661,"tags":662,"tldr":666,"updated":666,"url":667,"__hash__":668},"content\u002F從 JavaScript 角度學 Python\u002F從-JavaScript-角度學-Python-29-BeautifulSoup.md","從 JavaScript 角度學 Python(29) - BeautifulSoup","691102834",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":633},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,29,35,38,41,47,50,53,57,60,63,80,83,92,96,103,112,118,124,132,167,170,217,223,234,245,248,257,264,318,321,327,341,350,353,357,360,365,370,379,385,394,398,401,410,413,422,428,437,441,449,458,462,470,479,483,494,497,505,508,511,520,523,526,535,538,541,550,557,566,569,572,575,578,581,584,587,623,629],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"已經準備進入鐵人賽的尾巴，所以這一篇就來介紹一個很常見的套件，也就是 BeautifulSoup，而這套件也是爬蟲很常使用的套件，所以接下來就讓我們來學習使用 BeautifulSoup 吧。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"beautifulsoup","BeautifulSoup",[16,24,25],{},"Python 很常被用於網路爬蟲，其中最多人用的就是 BeautifulSoup 套件，那...BeautifulSoup 套件是什麼東西呢？",[16,27,28],{},"這邊就讓我們直接看維基百科對於 BeautifulSoup 的說明：",[30,31,32],"blockquote",{},[16,33,34],{},"Beautiful Soup是一個Python包，功能包括解析HTML、XML文件、修復含有未閉合標籤等錯誤的文件（此種文件常被稱為tag soup）。這個擴充包為待解析的頁面建立一棵樹，以便提取其中的資料，這在網路資料採集時非常有用。",[16,36,37],{},"透過上面解釋我們可以粗略知道 BeautifulSoup 主要是幫我們解析下載回來的 HTML 檔案套件，使用這個套件可以大大方便我們在擷取特定片段資料的方便性。",[16,39,40],{},"oh!對了，如果你有去查過 BeautifulSoup 的話，你會發現它的封面圖會是一個中世紀風格的圖片，而且你會發現它的圖片很特別：",[16,42,43],{},[44,45],"img",{"alt":22,"src":46},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E5%BE%9E%20JavaScript%20%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%B8%20Python\u002F202108302112.jpg",[16,48,49],{},"而 BeautifulSoup 這個名字是來自愛麗絲夢遊仙境的一首詩所命名的，所以有些翻譯文檔甚至會說這是一份「愛麗絲的文件」，這也就是為什麼 BeautifulSoup 套件封面圖片都會是中世紀的風格，畢竟愛麗絲夢遊仙境當時的背景設定是在中世紀歐洲(如果沒記錯的話)。",[16,51,52],{},"那前面這邊一開始只是簡單小聊一下 BeautifulSoup 套件有趣的地方，接下來就讓我們準備開始安裝 BeautifulSoup 吧！",[12,54,56],{"id":55},"安裝-beautifulsoup","安裝 BeautifulSoup",[16,58,59],{},"BeautifulSoup 在安裝上跟 Requests 套件較不同，比較不用擔心在 Python2 或是 Python3 版本上的套件名稱不同，因為在安裝 BeautifulSoup 的過程，都是相同的名稱。",[16,61,62],{},"Python2：",[64,65,70],"pre",{"className":66,"code":67,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"language-py shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","pip install beautifulsoup4\n","py","",[71,72,73],"code",{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,75,78],"span",{"class":76,"line":77},"line",1,[74,79,67],{},[16,81,82],{},"Python3：",[64,84,86],{"className":66,"code":85,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"pip3 install beautifulsoup4\n",[71,87,88],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,89,90],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,91,85],{},[12,93,95],{"id":94},"beautifulsoup-基本使用","BeautifulSoup 基本使用",[16,97,98,99,102],{},"當你安裝完畢之後，你可以先引入 BeautifulSoup 套件到你的 Python 專案中，但是這邊有一個很特別地方，BeautifulSoup 在安裝的時候，模組名稱會是 ",[71,100,101],{},"bs4"," ，所以通常我們在引入 BeautifulSoup 時都會重新命名一下：",[64,104,106],{"className":66,"code":105,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"from bs4 import BeautifulSoup # 這絕對不是你想像中的 Bootstrap4\n",[71,107,108],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,109,110],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,111,105],{},[16,113,114,115,117],{},"還是在提醒一次，這邊的 ",[71,116,101],{}," 絕對不是 Bootstrap4 而是 BeautifulSoup4！（很重要）",[16,119,120],{},[44,121],{"alt":122,"src":123},"請問 bs4 是哪一個的縮寫？","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E5%BE%9E%20JavaScript%20%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%B8%20Python\u002F%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E6%A2%97%E5%9C%96%E5%89%B5%E4%BD%9C-1632575908.png",[16,125,126,127,131],{},"接下來你可以嘗試貼入官方所提供的範例程式碼，而這又稱之為",[128,129,130],"strong",{},"愛麗絲文件","：",[64,133,135],{"className":66,"code":134,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"from bs4 import BeautifulSoup\n\nhtml_doc = \"\"\"\n\u003Chtml>\u003Chead>\u003Ctitle>The Dormouse's story\u003C\u002Ftitle>\u003C\u002Fhead>\u003Cbody>\u003Cp class=\"title\">\u003Cb>The Dormouse's story\u003C\u002Fb>\u003C\u002Fp>\u003Cp class=\"story\">Once upon a time there were three little sisters; and their names were\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Felsie\" class=\"sister\" id=\"link1\">Elsie\u003C\u002Fa>,\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Flacie\" class=\"sister\" id=\"link2\">Lacie\u003C\u002Fa> and\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Ftillie\" class=\"sister\" id=\"link3\">Tillie\u003C\u002Fa>;and they lived at the bottom of a well.\u003C\u002Fp>\u003Cp class=\"story\">...\u003C\u002Fp>\n\"\"\"\n",[71,136,137,142,149,155,161],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,138,139],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,140,141],{},"from bs4 import BeautifulSoup\n",[74,143,145],{"class":76,"line":144},2,[74,146,148],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":147},true,"\n",[74,150,152],{"class":76,"line":151},3,[74,153,154],{},"html_doc = \"\"\"\n",[74,156,158],{"class":76,"line":157},4,[74,159,160],{},"\u003Chtml>\u003Chead>\u003Ctitle>The Dormouse's story\u003C\u002Ftitle>\u003C\u002Fhead>\u003Cbody>\u003Cp class=\"title\">\u003Cb>The Dormouse's story\u003C\u002Fb>\u003C\u002Fp>\u003Cp class=\"story\">Once upon a time there were three little sisters; and their names were\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Felsie\" class=\"sister\" id=\"link1\">Elsie\u003C\u002Fa>,\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Flacie\" class=\"sister\" id=\"link2\">Lacie\u003C\u002Fa> and\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Ftillie\" class=\"sister\" id=\"link3\">Tillie\u003C\u002Fa>;and they lived at the bottom of a well.\u003C\u002Fp>\u003Cp class=\"story\">...\u003C\u002Fp>\n",[74,162,164],{"class":76,"line":163},5,[74,165,166],{},"\"\"\"\n",[16,168,169],{},"那麼我們可以看到上面的 HTML 是被壓縮過的，因此是非常難以閱讀的，但是 BeautifulSoup 它可以將壓縮過的 HTML 結構轉換成標準的 HTML 縮排形式，也就是身為前端工程師可以讀懂的格式，而用法也非常簡單，只需要這樣寫就可以囉",[64,171,173],{"className":66,"code":172,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"from bs4 import BeautifulSoup\n\nhtml_doc = \"\"\"\n\u003Chtml>\u003Chead>\u003Ctitle>The Dormouse's story\u003C\u002Ftitle>\u003C\u002Fhead>\u003Cbody>\u003Cp class=\"title\">\u003Cb>The Dormouse's story\u003C\u002Fb>\u003C\u002Fp>\u003Cp class=\"story\">Once upon a time there were three little sisters; and their names were\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Felsie\" class=\"sister\" id=\"link1\">Elsie\u003C\u002Fa>,\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Flacie\" class=\"sister\" id=\"link2\">Lacie\u003C\u002Fa> and\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Ftillie\" class=\"sister\" id=\"link3\">Tillie\u003C\u002Fa>;and they lived at the bottom of a well.\u003C\u002Fp>\u003Cp class=\"story\">...\u003C\u002Fp>\n\"\"\"\n\nsoup = BeautifulSoup(html_doc, 'html.parser')\n\nprint(soup.prettify())\n",[71,174,175,179,183,187,191,195,200,206,211],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,176,177],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,178,141],{},[74,180,181],{"class":76,"line":144},[74,182,148],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":147},[74,184,185],{"class":76,"line":151},[74,186,154],{},[74,188,189],{"class":76,"line":157},[74,190,160],{},[74,192,193],{"class":76,"line":163},[74,194,166],{},[74,196,198],{"class":76,"line":197},6,[74,199,148],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":147},[74,201,203],{"class":76,"line":202},7,[74,204,205],{},"soup = BeautifulSoup(html_doc, 'html.parser')\n",[74,207,209],{"class":76,"line":208},8,[74,210,148],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":147},[74,212,214],{"class":76,"line":213},9,[74,215,216],{},"print(soup.prettify())\n",[16,218,219],{},[44,220],{"alt":221,"src":222},"結果","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E5%BE%9E%20JavaScript%20%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%B8%20Python\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-09-25%2021.25.12(1).png",[16,224,225,226,229,230,233],{},"那這邊我們可以看到其中一行是 ",[71,227,228],{},"soup = BeautifulSoup(html_doc, 'html.parser')"," 這一行的第二個參數其實是告訴 BeautifulSoup 要使用哪一種解析器來解析 HTML，基本上在官方網站上都有說明建議你使用哪一種解析器，以官方建議來講，會建議你使用 ",[71,231,232],{},"lxml"," 的解析器，如果你要使用這個解析器的話就必須額外安裝：",[64,235,239],{"className":236,"code":237,"language":238,"meta":69,"style":69},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","pip3 install lxml\n","cmd",[71,240,241],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,242,243],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,244,237],{},[16,246,247],{},"安裝完畢之後記得調整一下解析器：",[64,249,251],{"className":66,"code":250,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"soup = BeautifulSoup(html_doc, 'lxml')\n",[71,252,253],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,254,255],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,256,250],{},[16,258,259,260,263],{},"最後你可以看到 ",[71,261,262],{},"print()"," 輸出一個非常標準且整理過的 HTML，或許終端機你會覺得很難閱讀，所以你也可以使用前面所學到的檔案寫入這個技巧來生成一個 HTML 檔案：",[64,265,267],{"className":66,"code":266,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"from bs4 import BeautifulSoup\n\nhtml_doc = \"\"\"\n\u003Chtml>\u003Chead>\u003Ctitle>The Dormouse's story\u003C\u002Ftitle>\u003C\u002Fhead>\u003Cbody>\u003Cp class=\"title\">\u003Cb>The Dormouse's story\u003C\u002Fb>\u003C\u002Fp>\u003Cp class=\"story\">Once upon a time there were three little sisters; and their names were\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Felsie\" class=\"sister\" id=\"link1\">Elsie\u003C\u002Fa>,\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Flacie\" class=\"sister\" id=\"link2\">Lacie\u003C\u002Fa> and\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Ftillie\" class=\"sister\" id=\"link3\">Tillie\u003C\u002Fa>;and they lived at the bottom of a well.\u003C\u002Fp>\u003Cp class=\"story\">...\u003C\u002Fp>\n\"\"\"\n\nsoup = BeautifulSoup(html_doc, 'lxml')\n\nf = open('index.html', 'w')\nf.write(soup.prettify())\nf.close()\n",[71,268,269,273,277,281,285,289,293,297,301,306,312],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,270,271],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,272,141],{},[74,274,275],{"class":76,"line":144},[74,276,148],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":147},[74,278,279],{"class":76,"line":151},[74,280,154],{},[74,282,283],{"class":76,"line":157},[74,284,160],{},[74,286,287],{"class":76,"line":163},[74,288,166],{},[74,290,291],{"class":76,"line":197},[74,292,148],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":147},[74,294,295],{"class":76,"line":202},[74,296,250],{},[74,298,299],{"class":76,"line":208},[74,300,148],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":147},[74,302,303],{"class":76,"line":213},[74,304,305],{},"f = open('index.html', 'w')\n",[74,307,309],{"class":76,"line":308},10,[74,310,311],{},"f.write(soup.prettify())\n",[74,313,315],{"class":76,"line":314},11,[74,316,317],{},"f.close()\n",[16,319,320],{},"屆時你再去打開 index.html 就會很好閱讀了，畢竟你是一名前端工程師對吧？",[16,322,323],{},[44,324],{"alt":325,"src":326},"快給我說「對」","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E5%BE%9E%20JavaScript%20%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%B8%20Python\u002F1632577437057.png",[16,328,329,330,333,334,337,338,131],{},"那麼基本上我們所有的操作都會跟 ",[71,331,332],{},"BeautifulSoup(html_doc, 'html.parser')"," 處理後的 ",[71,335,336],{},"soup"," 操作有關，舉例你想取得 HTML 結構中的 ",[71,339,340],{},"title",[64,342,344],{"className":66,"code":343,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"print(soup.title) # \u003Ctitle>The Dormouse's story\u003C\u002Ftitle>\n",[71,345,346],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,347,348],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,349,343],{},[16,351,352],{},"那麼 BeautifulSoup 還有哪些東西呢？這邊就讓我們繼續了解它吧！",[12,354,356],{"id":355},"搜尋-html-元素","搜尋 HTML 元素",[16,358,359],{},"BeautifulSoup 提供相當多的方法可以針對 HTML 標籤去搜尋，那這邊也讓我們每一個都嘗試看看。",[361,362,364],"h3",{"id":363},"find_all","find_all()",[16,366,367,369],{},[71,368,364],{}," 可以用於搜尋複數的 HTML 元素：",[64,371,373],{"className":66,"code":372,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"print(soup.find_all('a')) # [\u003Ca class=\"sister\" href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Felsie\" id=\"link1\">Elsie\u003C\u002Fa>, \u003Ca class=\"sister\" href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Flacie\" id=\"link2\">Lacie\u003C\u002Fa>, \u003Ca class=\"sister\" href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Ftillie\" id=\"link3\">Tillie\u003C\u002Fa>]\n",[71,374,375],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,376,377],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,378,372],{},[16,380,381,382,384],{},"其中 ",[71,383,363],{}," 也可以針對 HTML 的屬性來搜尋：",[64,386,388],{"className":66,"code":387,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"print(soup.find_all('a', { 'id': 'link3' })) # [\u003Ca class=\"sister\" href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Ftillie\" id=\"link3\">Tillie\u003C\u002Fa>]\n",[71,389,390],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,391,392],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,393,387],{},[361,395,397],{"id":396},"select","select()",[16,399,400],{},"那麼有特別針對 HTML 元素搜尋的方式，也就會有特別針對 CSS 選擇器的方式搜尋 HTML 元素，首先是針對 ID 的方式：",[64,402,404],{"className":66,"code":403,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"print(soup.select('#link1')) # [\u003Ca class=\"sister\" href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Felsie\" id=\"link1\">Elsie\u003C\u002Fa>]\n",[71,405,406],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,407,408],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,409,403],{},[16,411,412],{},"另一種則是針對 class 搜尋：",[64,414,416],{"className":66,"code":415,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"print(soup.select('.story')) # [\u003Cp class=\"story\">Once upon a time there were three little sisters; and their names were\u003Ca class=\"sister\" href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Felsie\" id=\"link1\">Elsie\u003C\u002Fa>,\u003Ca class=\"sister\" href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Flacie\" id=\"link2\">Lacie\u003C\u002Fa> and\u003Ca class=\"sister\" href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Ftillie\" id=\"link3\">Tillie\u003C\u002Fa>;and they lived at the bottom of a well.\u003C\u002Fp>, \u003Cp class=\"story\">...\u003C\u002Fp>]\n",[71,417,418],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,419,420],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,421,415],{},[16,423,424,425,427],{},"oh!題外話一下，",[71,426,396],{}," 也可以直接針對 HTMl 標籤搜尋唷",[64,429,431],{"className":66,"code":430,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"print(soup.select('b')) # [\u003Cb>The Dormouse's story\u003C\u002Fb>]\n",[71,432,433],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,434,435],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,436,430],{},[361,438,440],{"id":439},"find","find()",[16,442,443,445,446,448],{},[71,444,440],{}," 雖然跟 ",[71,447,439],{}," 感覺很像，但是它主要是回傳一個符合條件的元素：",[64,450,452],{"className":66,"code":451,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"print(soup.find_all('a')) # \u003Ca class=\"sister\" href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Felsie\" id=\"link1\">Elsie\u003C\u002Fa>\n",[71,453,454],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,455,456],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,457,451],{},[361,459,461],{"id":460},"select_one","select_one()",[16,463,464,466,467,469],{},[71,465,461],{}," 從名稱來講也很明顯的知道跟 ",[71,468,439],{}," 很像，只會回傳第一個符合的元素：",[64,471,473],{"className":66,"code":472,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"print(soup.select('.story')) # print(soup.select_one('.story')) # \u003Cp class=\"story\">Once upon a time there were three little sisters; and their names were\u003Ca class=\"sister\" href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Felsie\" id=\"link1\">Elsie\u003C\u002Fa>,\u003Ca class=\"sister\" href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Flacie\" id=\"link2\">Lacie\u003C\u002Fa> and\u003Ca class=\"sister\" href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Ftillie\" id=\"link3\">Tillie\u003C\u002Fa>;and they lived at the bottom of a well.\u003C\u002Fp>\n",[71,474,475],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,476,477],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,478,472],{},[12,480,482],{"id":481},"取出-html-內容","取出 HTML 內容",[16,484,485,486,489,490,493],{},"前面我們知道如何取得我們要的元素之後，那該怎麼取出 HTML 元素中的東西呢？例如取出 HTML 元素中的文字，舉例來講 ",[71,487,488],{},"\u003Cb>The Dormouse's story\u003C\u002Fb>"," 中的 ",[71,491,492],{},"The Dormouse's story"," 這一段文字。",[16,495,496],{},"那這邊將會使用前面的這一段範例：",[64,498,499],{"className":66,"code":372,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},[71,500,501],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,502,503],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,504,372],{},[361,506,507],{"id":507},"text",[16,509,510],{},"這個語法非常簡單，可以直接取出 HTML 的文字：",[64,512,514],{"className":66,"code":513,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"print(soup.find_all('a')[0].text) # Elsie\n",[71,515,516],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,517,518],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,519,513],{},[361,521,522],{"id":522},"attrs",[16,524,525],{},"接下來是如果你想要取出 HTML 的屬性的話，可以使用這個方法，但是要注意它會回傳一個字典：",[64,527,529],{"className":66,"code":528,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"print(soup.find_all('a')[0].attrs) # {'href': 'http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Felsie', 'class': ['sister'], 'id': 'link1'}\n",[71,530,531],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,532,533],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,534,528],{},[361,536,537],{"id":537},"target",[16,539,540],{},"當然如果你不想要回傳那麼一個物件的話，可以直接指定屬性回傳：",[64,542,544],{"className":66,"code":543,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"print(soup.find_all('a')[0]['href']) # http:\u002F\u002Fexample.com\u002Felsie\n",[71,545,546],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,547,548],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,549,543],{},[16,551,552,553,556],{},"題外話一下，如果你是使用 ",[71,554,555],{},"get"," 方法的話，若這個屬性不存在則也是可以的唷~",[64,558,560],{"className":66,"code":559,"language":68,"meta":69,"style":69},"print(soup.find_all('a')[0].get('title', '我不存在')) # 我不存在\n",[71,561,562],{"__ignoreMap":69},[74,563,564],{"class":76,"line":77},[74,565,559],{},[16,567,568],{},"那這邊這邊就只列出我常用的 BeautifulSoup 方法，實際上如果想看更詳細的會建議可以看官方文件唷~",[12,570,571],{"id":571},"作者的話",[16,573,574],{},"這幾天跟朋友聊天聊到自己以前做版本控制的做法...",[16,576,577],{},"日期＋版本號這種方式，結果結案的時候變成...",[16,579,580],{},"20130307_v1.zip\n20130307_v2.zip\n20130307_v3.zip\n20130307_v4.zip\n20130307_v5.zip\n...",[16,582,583],{},"真慶幸自己學會使用 Git 之後這種狀況就沒有出現了。",[12,585,586],{"id":586},"關於兔兔們",[588,589,590,600,608,616],"ul",{},[591,592,593],"li",{},[594,595,599],"a",{"href":596,"rel":597},"https:\u002F\u002Ftailwindcss.tw",[598],"nofollow","Tailwind CSS 臺灣官網",[591,601,602,607],{},[594,603,606],{"href":604,"rel":605},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.facebook.com\u002Ftailwindcss.tw",[598],"Tailwind CSS 臺灣"," (臉書粉絲專頁)",[591,609,610,615],{},[594,611,614],{"href":612,"rel":613},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.facebook.com\u002Fgroups\u002Ftailwindcss.taiwan",[598],"兔兔教 × Tailwind CSS Taiwan"," (臉書社群)",[591,617,618],{},[594,619,622],{"href":620,"rel":621},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.facebook.com\u002Flalarabbits-%E5%